AIM:
To extract deleted files from the disk using PowerData Recovery tool.

PROCEDURE:

Step 1: Download MiniTool PowerData Recovery tool from             
     https://www.minitool.com/data-recovery-software/free-for-windows.html 
Step 2: Install it and set up the Tool.
Step 3: Now Create a File anywhere and Delete it in Disks. Make Sure the File 
            has been Permanently deleted from Recycle Bin. 
Step 4: Open the MiniTool Recovery tool and Scan the Disk where the File has 
            been Deleted.

 


Step 5: Choose the Deleted Files Folder, which will recover the File and display  
             it in the list.
 

Step 6: Double-click to view and Save that File Tick the CheckBox and choose 
            the Save button.
